<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>result</title>
    <style>
        .box{
            background-color: white;
            border: 1px solid lightgray;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center; 
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            height: 20px;

        }
        .n1{
            color: orange;
        }
        .n2{
            color: red;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .n3{
            color:aqua;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .n4{
            color: cadetblue;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h2>결과 확인하기</h2>
    <h3><span class="n1"><%=userinfo.name%></span> 님 환영합니다!</h3>
    <div class="box">성별: <%=userinfo.gender%> </div>
    <div class="box">생년월일: <%=userinfo.calender%> </div>
    <div class="box">관심사: <%=userinfo.favorite%></div>
    <hr>
    
    <% if(addInfo){ %>
        <h3>다른 태그 작성해보기</h3>
        <span>좋아하는 색깔 : <span class="n2"><%=userinfo.color%></span></span>
        <br>
        <br>
    
        <span>좋아하는 숫자 : <span class="n3"><%=userinfo.number%></span></span>
        <br>
        <br>
    
        <span>다짐한마디 : <span class="n4"><%=userinfo.comment%></span></span>
    <%}%>
    <script>
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded",function(){
            const colorSpan = document.querySelector(".n2");
            colorSpan.style.color = "<%=userinfo.color%>"
        })
    </script>
   
    <br>
    <br>

    <a href="/practice01">실습문제 1로 이동하기</a>
    <br>
    <a href="/practice02">실습문제 2로 이동하기</a>
    
    
</body>
</html>